  "identifier": "HB 33",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to data privacy.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 367.3611 to define \"automated-decision system,\" \"base price,\" \"individualized data,\" and \"surveillance pricing\"; amend KRS 367.3617 to prohibit any controller under the Kentucky Consumer Data Protection Act from engaging in surveillance pricing, or offering, setting, or displaying a price for a good or service to a consumer using an automated-decision system that is based, in whole or in part, on individualized data; provide that the Act may be cited as the Kentucky Price Fairness Act.",
